To implement join operation of databases

eg. select * from emp, dept where emp.deptid = dept.deptid

Input Files Schema:
emp: (ename, empid (PK), deptid)
dept: (deptid (PK), dname)

Input:
EMP file:			DEPT file:
josh,1,1			1,hadoop
armanda,2,2			2,cassandra
alex,3,2			3,mongodb
ladan,4,1			4,hive
mike,5,3
penny,6,2

